  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It's a nice sunny day in Tor Borgh and aimless lout Geoff Dandy is woken up by his best mate Dolph Dombardo raging incoherently about going to the Jiggly Swamp. Saving Dolph from doom sets in motion events that lead to one question...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >What is the Crypt of Darkness?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GENRE</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Old School Inspired RPG Nostalgia</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>GAME INFO</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Classic RPG gameplay with a Shining Force inspired tactics battle system. Level up system allows you to customize your character stats.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PROS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108630/extras/3116361b9eeb19dcc8b9cf917aa7fbd4.webp?t=1728808222\" width=12 height=12 /></span>  Characters and events change as the adventure unfolds.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108630/extras/3116361b9eeb19dcc8b9cf917aa7fbd4.webp?t=1728808222\" width=12 height=12 /></span>  Strategy battle system inspired by Shining Force.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108630/extras/3116361b9eeb19dcc8b9cf917aa7fbd4.webp?t=1728808222\" width=12 height=12 /></span>  No yappers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>CONS</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108630/extras/b44c04650166727dfcaa914e671f5cc7.webp?t=1728808222\" width=12 height=12 /></span>  4 hour play time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108630/extras/b44c04650166727dfcaa914e671f5cc7.webp?t=1728808222\" width=12 height=12 /></span>  Needlessly complicated plot.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1108630/extras/b44c04650166727dfcaa914e671f5cc7.webp?t=1728808222\" width=12 height=12 /></span>  Not retro style.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
